OL,3,C'Heartbreaking': Classroom not big
OL,4,Cenough for disabled boy's wheelchair
OL,6,FKatie Oscroft reports.
OL,8,FThe mother of a boy with complex
OL,9,Fspecial needs says it is
OL,10,F"heartbreaking" that he is unable to
OL,11,Fattend his allocated school because it
OL,12,Fis too small for his mobility
OL,13,Fequipment.
OL,15,FFive-year-old Phoenix Ray, from
OL,16,FChesterfield, has cerebral palsy and
OL,17,Fis unable to speak after being born
OL,18,Fprematurely and suffering brain damage.
