OL,3,C'Heartbreaking': Classroom not big
OL,4,Cenough for disabled boy's wheelchair
OL,6,FHe relies on a wheelchair to get
OL,7,Faround, but was denied a place in
OL,8,Fspecial education and instead told he
OL,9,Fcould attend Highfield Hall Primary
OL,10,FSchool.
OL,12,FHis mother Cally Hewer, 39, said the
OL,13,Fmainstream school made extra efforts
OL,14,Fto accommodate him, without success.
OL,16,F"The school tried their best, but to
OL,17,Fbe told he just won't fit inside the
OL,18,Fclassroom is heartbreaking," she said.
