OL,3,C'Heartbreaking': Classroom not big
OL,4,Cenough for disabled boy's wheelchair
OL,6,FPhoenix is now being kept at home with
OL,7,Fhis two-year-old sister, Nelly, until
OL,8,Fa suitable place is found.
OL,10,F"We've gone through so much, it was a
OL,11,Fchallenging birth, and he fought so
OL,12,Fhard just to have a life and to me
OL,13,Fthat life should be fulfilling," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"We shouldn't face barrier after
OL,17,Fbarrier."
