OL,6,FThe case comes after an ITV News
OL,7,Finvestigation revealed the shocking
OL,8,Fscale of the special educational needs
OL,9,Fcrisis across UK.
OL,11,FDerbyshire County Council said it had
OL,12,Finvested #1million to improve its
OL,13,Feducation, health and care plan (EHCP)
OL,14,Fassessment process and #11million to
OL,15,Fcreate 500 additional special needs
OL,16,Fschool places.
OL,18,FA spokesperson said an assessment of
OL,19,FPhoenix's case "should have worked in
OL,20,Fa more timely manner".
